The '''British Journal of American Legal Studies''' is a [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] journal devoted to [[United States law]], based in the [[United Kingdom]]. It was founded in 2012, and publishes articles related to [[constitutional law]] having in the United States, including [[human rights]], legal and [[Political philosophy|political theory]], socio-legal studies and legal history.

