{{Expand Spanish|Constitución española de 1876|date=May 2013}}
The '''Spanish Constitution of 1876''' ({{lang-es|Constitucion Española}}), was the [[constitution]] enacted after the [[Spain under the Restoration|restoration]] of the [[Monarchy of Spain|Spanish monarchy]]. It came into effect on 30 June 1876.

